feat(observability): spans manuais, propagacao OTel via fila, admin DLQ

Tracing helpers (observability/tracing.ts):
- withSpan(name, attrs, fn): wrapper que cuida de recordException + status
  ERROR + end(); silencia erros de tipagem ao setar atributos undefined
- injectContext()/extractContext(): serializa contexto W3C Trace Context
  num carrier para anexar ao payload do job e propagar ao worker

Cache (services/cache.ts):
- getWithSingleFlight agora abre span 'cache.get' com cache.key, cache.status
  (hit/miss/hit_after_wait), cache.lock (acquired/waiting/wait_timeout)
- Sub-span 'cache.loader' quando carregamos da fonte original

Checkout (services/checkout.ts):
- Span raiz 'checkout.process' com idempotency.outcome, order.id,
  checkout.outcome (accepted | rejected_<reason>) e item_count
- Sub-spans: idempotency.claim, checkout.tx, stock.reserve, queue.enqueue
- Metricas faltantes adicionadas: checkout_duration_seconds{phase=reserve_stock}
  e checkout_duration_seconds{phase=enqueue}
- Job payload agora carrega _otel com traceparent W3C

Worker (workers/checkout-worker.ts):
- Extrai _otel do job e usa otelContext.with(parentCtx) para garantir que
  worker.process aparece como continuacao do MESMO traceId do request HTTP
- Sub-spans: erp.invoice, orders.mark_confirmed
- Atributos: order.id, queue.job_id, queue.attempt, erp.invoice_id

Admin (routes/admin.ts):
- GET /admin/dlq?limit=N: lista contents da DLQ para inspecao operacional
  (primeira chamada do runbook quando dlq_size > 0)
- POST /admin/queue/gauges/refresh: trigger manual de refresh dos gauges
- Em producao requer auth dedicada (registrado no README como simplificacao)

Validado E2E:
- Trace de checkout aceito: 5 spans no API (idempotency.claim, stock.reserve,
  checkout.tx, queue.enqueue, checkout.process) + 3 spans no worker
  (erp.invoice, orders.mark_confirmed, worker.process), TODOS com o MESMO
  traceId atravessando o limite assincrono BullMQ.
- Trace de falha: ERP_FAILURE_RATE=1 -> 5 tentativas com backoff exp
  (1+2+4+8+16=31s) -> order=failed -> DLQ size=1 com traceparent preservado.
